trans-unit.target: Great Fortune<tab>Thou shalt experience extraordinary fortune. Keep these words of guidance in thy heart.
Good Fortune<tab>Thou shalt experience exceptional fortune. Keep these words of guidance in thy heart.
Fair Fortune<tab>Thou shalt experience moderate fortune. Keep these words of guidance in thy heart.
Small Fortune<tab>Thou shalt experience limited fortune. Keep these words of guidance in thy heart.
Misfortune<tab>Thou shalt experience misfortune. Heed these words of guidance, and thy luck may change.
Grave Misfortune<tab>Thou shalt experience considerable misfortune. Heed these words of guidance, and thy luck may change.
